{%- comment -%}
  Ganguram — Product-card "Buy now" config (Phase 2.11D.1).

  Publishes window.GanguramProductCardBuyConfig and loads
  assets/ganguram-product-card-buy.js + .css. The "Buy now" button (rendered only
  on single-variant product cards by snippets/quick-buy.liquid) reuses the theme's
  existing AJAX add, then proceeds to checkout ONLY when the cart-side MOV /
  checkout guard allows; otherwise it opens the cart drawer with the minimum-order
  notice. No Shopify checkout / final shipping-charge / ShipZip / SBZ / zipLogic /
  resolver / settings_data.json change. Fail-open.

  Loaded AFTER ganguram-delivery-progress-config so window.GanguramDeliveryProgress
  (the guard) is available.
{%- endcomment -%}
<script>
  window.GanguramProductCardBuyConfig = {
    cartUrl: {{ routes.cart_url | json }},
    checkoutUrl: "/checkout"
  };
</script>
{{ 'ganguram-product-card-buy.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
<script src="{{ 'ganguram-product-card-buy.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
